- Taxa de Poupança UI (`src/lib/diagnostico.ts`) is #111 scope, not on `feat/opencode-v2` (source: branch diff) — handled: prove exclusion via `totaisReceitaDespesa` + explicit sobra/taxa arithmetic in `__tests__/saldo.test.ts`, not diagnostico page.
